info.name: Music Streaming API Test SuiteðŸŽ§
info.description:
# ðŸš€ What?

This suite includes the collection of test sets to test the Music Streaming API managed in several parts -

- User Management
    
- Song Management
    
- Playlist Management
    
- Music Discovery & Social Features
    
- Stream Songs and Playback History

item.name: User Management

request.description: Register the user in the system
Login the user and start the session
Retrieves the profile of the logged-in user

item.description:
POST `api/auth/signup`: Register a new user.

POST `api/auth/login`: Authenticate a user.

GET `api/profile/{username}`: Get user profile details.

PUT `api/profile/{username}`: Update user profile details.

request.description: Retrieves the song with given Id
Search song based on title, artist, album, genre

item.description:
GET `api/songs`: Get all the songs.

GET `api/songs/search?queyParam=value`: Search for songs by criteria like title, artist, album, genre.

GET `api/songs/{id}`: Get details of a specific song.

item.name: Playlist Management

request.description: Create the playlist with given name for the logged-in user
Add the song to the playlist
Retrieve all playlist of the user
Retrieve the playlist based on Id
Shuffle the songs in the playlist

item.description:
- POST `api/playlists/create` endpoint allows users to create a new playlist by providing the playlist name and username.
    
- POST `api/playlists/{playlistId}/addSong` endpoint allows users to add songs to a playlist.
    
- DELETE `api/playlists/{playlistId}/removeSong` endpoint allows users to remove song from a playlist specified by playlistId.
    
- GET `api/playlists/user/{username}` endpoint retrieves all playlists for a specific user.
    
- GET `api/playlists/{playlistId}` endpoint retrieves a playlist by its ID.
    
- GET `api/playlists/{playlistId}/shuffle` endpoint shuffles the song in the playlist

item.name: Music Discovery & Social Features

request.description: Recommends 10 songs based on the users playback history

item.description:
- GET `api/discover/recommend/genre` endpoint returns song recommendations based on the genre.
    
- GET `api/discover/recommend/user/{username}` endpoint returns recommendations for a specific user.
    
- POST `api/discover/followArtist` endpoint allows a user to follow an artist.
    
- GET `api/discover/recommendations` endpoint return the recommendations for a user based on playback history

- **POST** **`api/artists`**: Create a new artist.
    
- **GET** **`api/artists`**: Retrieve all artists.
    
- **GET** **`api/artists/{id}`**: Retrieve a specific artist by ID.
    
- **GET** **`api/artists/search?name=value`**: Search for artists by name.
